column6: - What on Earth has made runaway Angela return to grimy old Earth? - Is it fighting? It's probably fighting. It's usually fighting. You know what she's like. - (Spoilers: It's not fighting. More spoilers: it does involve fighting, but she honestly wasn't planning it, no, really, honest.)
